Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}SAI終端服務一般被稱為回收方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在世界各地共有29個部門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我所就職的第一終端服務 負責管轄總部所在的遠東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這之後又要去總部開會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胃又痛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉可以幫我泡杯茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長 別老是把艾拉當作泡茶的使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在她可是司的執行者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請在這裡簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只不過是還沒改掉習慣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唷 諸位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}縹康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的觀測者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別看那樣 他可是在這裡工作快十年的老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這小子 放著工作不做去哪裡偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然是帶薪休假或者出差什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來去女人那裡叫做出差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我還是第一次這樣聽說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記住這個絕不會吃虧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝君那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真棒 艾拉你泡的茶依然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉組隊的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我叫水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是那個啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和伍堂部長打招呼 照顧進來的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說你啊 和部長是什麼樣的關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請一定要告訴我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為得了闌尾炎結果應試失敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有必要就不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感謝你的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次是特例
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 如果我認為你並不適合在我們公司工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會立刻開除你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}記住了嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}部長和我父親認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和你有點話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉～ 我的搭檔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 再多來點笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們這裡的女孩子 為什麼表情都這麼可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是因為你這幾天丟下工作不管的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}關於這個 還希望你可以充分的說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 但是我肚子有點餓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想先去吃點東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個笑話可真是好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要太緊張 放鬆點好好幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}救命啊…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是柳豐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們並不是可疑的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老實地將那邊的馬克思交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是終端服務 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}你們搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}馬克思快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂等等 為什麼要嚇唬他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯誤 我沒有聽清楚 請再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之先追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被他們跑掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來又要寫檢討了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們先回去了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這都第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三次…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經安排相當輕鬆的工作給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果三次都被拒簽同意書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有好好和艾拉建立了信賴關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}應該不會變成這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟是走後門的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不費一絲辛勞就進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 下次我會注意的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 司那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能確實說的太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿總是直言不諱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說完又開始後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 你和司吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘴上說著討厭討厭 其實很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}清清純純的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 我和司才不是這種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都說了不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得和平時沒什麼兩樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天下班後有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有空的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你有在喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一開始就說我還未成年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 你和艾拉有好好相處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不知道她在想什麼」之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能告訴我關於艾拉的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月以前和艾拉是搭檔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告訴你也沒有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果本人不去互相理解也是白費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也覺得很過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把她交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們這麼多的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也是因為艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然艾拉是那樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可要好好和她相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜託你這種事我也是醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我想和艾拉進一步搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這傢伙是蘿莉控嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老闆再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長和總部總說要提高什麼工作效率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就是胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也做了將近十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到現在也看不到正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誰知道到底該如何銷毀回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誰都不會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何銷毀回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有在聽嗎 新人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香 香月小姐 好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}耶 香月喝多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生怎麼也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是這裡的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這傢伙喝了多少杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有三杯左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說她酒量很差？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之我先送她回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經是常事了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 關門就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs30\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\pos(674,261)\frx16\fry8}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\c&H000000&\fs25\bord0\1a&H80&\frz7.458\frx18\fry8\pos(583,451)}\h\h\h\h\h\h單元測驗房\N[訓練]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}單元測驗房？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是哪裡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 總部大樓裡竟然還有這種設施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是艾拉的觀測者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是終端服務部的專屬工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是繪瑠 這位是鐵黑右次郎師父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請跪拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}無視我嗎 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在採集數據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}數據？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是在測量身體能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭 居然偷看少女的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是個糟糕的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她經常會來做這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 只是和小司搭檔之後才經常來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為最近負擔也變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保養的次數也增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒希望她能休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}負擔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為以前就只是倒倒茶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而現在回到現場工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情況當然是不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別光動嘴不動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 對不起 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過看起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}擅自跑過來看 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 我也沒有躲藏著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼突然要訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是在介意工作上的失誤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}時隔許久回到現場工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體沒能像想像中那樣行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的我在拖司的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是因為空檔期的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很快就會找回感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 不只是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和持有者溝通的時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像立刻就會變得很僵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖…因為沒有做暖機運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 暖機運轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是以前的汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的需要嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要解決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作為你的執行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能再給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果司已經覺得受不了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就只能解散我們的搭檔關係了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這人呢 其實很墨守成規的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作的話守規矩還是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以來這以後 我還是儘量試著讀懂規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是相當的應付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「臨機應變地對應」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「用最好的方法應對」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具體的內容一點都沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我能做的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}按照規則上寫的臨機應變地對應而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臨機應變？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如說 和持有者之間的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不讓艾拉來做 而讓我來做怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是觀測者的工作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}監督搭檔的執行者 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然我知道這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好不容易能成為搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互相幫助一下也挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在艾拉找回感覺之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依靠一下我這種人也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不要這樣試一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣決定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就盡力來制定自己的規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 我下次會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 滿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 你覺得司這人怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才…才沒有什麼奇怪的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和小司搭檔是不是成為你的負擔了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我感覺你最近很明顯地在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必對司這樣的新人太客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不願意的話就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你只是被課長強行和他組隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且…拖後腿的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙真是 果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗚嘎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然不向我如實彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「不找藉口才帥氣」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你難道是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我說過那麼多次 不要再把自己當學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿 不要太生司的氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 首先是傾聽對方的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是附和對方就能讓人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司在問我一些奇怪的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和回收對象的持有者交涉時 都需要注意些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底是無能還是蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這又怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾是有感情的 持有者也是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是從香月那裡現學現賣來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽著 僅僅回收吉芙提爾是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否則的話 我們的工作只能帶來悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要依順吉芙提爾和持有者雙方的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雙方都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概只有我們這裡會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就連本部也對這種方法避而不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 因為我是贊成香月的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以既然你來這裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就要實踐這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了 謝謝你教給我這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 塞克 要去工作了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 現在就去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真的有那麼要緊的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次對你說了很多過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿一大早就這麼激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定是到了複雜的年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我懂的 我家的女兒也是完全不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請別說那種令人悲傷的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 差不多就這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唷 真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太會使喚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在做自己用的工作手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼 比起我 艾拉更努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}單元測驗房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了找回在空白期裡丟失的感覺 每天都在進行訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 不管能不能找回感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冒冒失失的樣子大概是不會變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個孩子真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明知是徒勞 卻還是這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徒勞？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉就是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什麼意思呢 徒勞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…艾拉的身體測試數據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微瞥到過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是一直在下降？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對 不是因此才為了彌補空白期而進行訓練的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提爾和人類還有其他機器人一樣要學習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 吉芙提爾並沒有空白期的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們體內原本就沒有植入遺忘功能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以這到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎樣訓練都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉以後一直會是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子自己也應該明白才對
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是因為我太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才讓她那麼勉強自己的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝 我…會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被她那樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}柳豐先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們是SAI公司的終端服務人員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.56,0:22:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是來通知您馬克思的回收時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回收？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次讓您受驚了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要回收了啊 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次逃走了真是抱歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是司的報告書？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 他們兩個意外的很合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過還真是讓我吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你居然什麼都沒跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別裝了 你沒和他說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:23:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉所剩的壽命還有2000小時的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
